http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Tiruchirapalli/Power-shutdown-in-city-on-Tuesday/article13978377.ece

There will be no power supply in the following areas of the city from 9.45 a.m. to 2 p.m. on Tuesday owing to maintenance works to be taken up by the Tangedco at East Boulevard Road and Varaganeri sub-stations:East Boulevard Road, Gandhi Market, Manimandapa Salai, Fish Market, Krishnapuram Road, Valayalkara Street, Chinnakadai Veedhi, Big Bazaar Street, Devadhanam, Madhuram grounds, Andal Street, Bharathiar Street, Butterworth Road, Keezha Andal Street, Rockfort, Babu Road, Mahalakshmi Nagar, Dhanarathinam Nagar, Welders Nagar, Tharanallur, Alanganathapuram, Veeramanagaram, Lakshmipuram, Bypass Road, Varaganeri, Periyar Nagar, Pitchai Nagar, Vasantha Nagar, Chekkadi Bazaar, Periyapalayam, Town Station, Arulanandapuram,Annai Nagar, Malligaipuram, Kezhapudur, Khajapettai, Pasumadam, Padaiyatchi Street, and Dharmanathapuram.